<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>1 Dollar Proof • Small Makes Big</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
      background: #0a0a0a;
      color: #eeeeee;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      text-align: center;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .hero {
      background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.75), rgba(0,0,0,0.85)), url('https://i.imgur.com/твоя_ссылка_на_картинку.jpg') center/cover no-repeat;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-direction: column;
      padding: 40px 20px;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 3.5rem;
      margin: 0 0 20px 0;
      color: #ffd700;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 1.35rem;
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: 15px auto;
    }
    .address-box {
      background: #1f1f1f;
      padding: 25px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      margin: 35px auto;
      max-width: 640px;
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      word-break: break-all;
      border: 1px solid #333;
    }
    button {
      background: #ffd700;
      color: #000;
      border: none;
      padding: 18px 50px;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      border-radius: 50px;
      cursor: pointer;
      margin: 20px 10px;
    }
    button:hover {
      background: #ffed4e;
    }
    .footer-text {
      margin-top: 60px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      opacity: 0.75;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="hero">
    <h1>1 Dollar Proof</h1>
    <p>One dollar from a millionaire.<br>Proof that from small you can make something big.</p>
    
    <p>You are under no obligation.<br>
    You can scroll past and do nothing.<br>
    But if you send exactly <strong>1 USDC</strong>, you become part of a simple experiment<br>
    that shows the world: even the smallest amount in many hands creates something meaningful.</p>
    
    <div class="address-box">
      Send <strong>exactly 1 USDC</strong> to this address:<br><br>
      <strong>EtRMBAKz6bmzHDK9ZkjAofyky63DQK8DVSCjdugm3DfX</strong>
    </div>
    
    <button onclick="copyAddress()">Copy Address</button>
    
    <div class="footer-text">
      No registration • No personal data • No obligations<br>
      The choice is always yours.
    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    function copyAddress() {
      navigator.clipboard.writeText("EtRMBAKz6bmzHDK9ZkjAofyky63DQK8DVSCjdugm3DfX");
      alert("✅ Address copied!\nSend exactly 1 USDC to this address.");
    }
  </script>
</body>
</html>
